        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ammonio Valentiniano <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>dup</abbr><ex>lario</ex></expan> militi <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>qui vixit <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXXVII <lb n="4"/>stupendiorum <note>sic</note> XX Valeria <lb n="5"/>Valerina coniugi <lb n="6"/>karissimo faciendum <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophag, ohne Deckel. Inschriftfeld mit gewelltem Rahmendekor, sog. &amp;apos;Barockmotiv&amp;apos;. Links neben dem Inschriftfeld Satyr; rechts Mänade. Z. 1 befindet sich oberhalb des gerahmten Inschriftfeldes. Z. 8 C mittig zentriert.</p>
            </div>
